<item>
            <title>[SPARK-24013] ApproximatePercentile grinds to a halt on sorted input.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-24013</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;select approx_percentile(rid, array(0.1)) from (select rand() as rid from range(10000000))&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).collect()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;takes 7 seconds, while&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;select approx_percentile(id, array(0.1)) from range(10000000)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).collect()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;grinds to a halt - processes the first million rows quickly, and then slows down to a few thousands rows / second (4m rows processed after 20 minutes).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thread dumps show that it spends time in QuantileSummary.compress.&lt;br/&gt;
Seems it hits some edge case inefficiency when dealing with sorted data?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
